Alright, come on.

00:03:29.267 --> 00:03:34.264
These are 5 beds that we purchased with money that you raised.

00:03:34.264 --> 00:03:37.561
Got some pillows, it's a really big deal Savannah, you did that.

00:03:37.561 --> 00:03:40.365
A lot of people last year have really big fancy jobs and they

00:03:40.365 --> 00:03:42.955
didn't do anything near as cool as that, so thank you

00:03:42.955 --> 00:03:45.122
for your compassion project and this is the president

